📘 Features of Selenium
Selenium is one of the most popular tools for automation testing because of its powerful and flexible features.

⭐ Main Features of Selenium
1. Supports multiple Programming languages
2. Multi-browser support
3. Cross-platform support
4. Parallel test execution
5. Handles pop-ups and alerts
6. Large community support
7. Integration with testing framework
8. Flexible and Extendable
9. Record & playback
10. Write once , Run anywhere
11. Easy to use
12. Lightweight tool
13. Opensource and Free
14. Cloud testing Support
15. Fast Performance
